{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_M3zBxcxtVOA55ibjHmD9WCD4","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package com.aiadvent.mcp.backend.notes.tool;\n     2→\n     3→import org.springframework.ai.tool.ToolCallbackProvider;\n     4→import org.springframework.ai.tool.method.MethodToolCallbackProvider;\n     5→import org.springframework.context.annotation.Bean;\n     6→import org.springframework.context.annotation.Configuration;\n     7→\n     8→@Configuration\n     9→class NotesToolConfiguration {\n    10→\n    11→  @Bean\n    12→  ToolCallbackProvider notesToolCallbackProvider(NotesTools notesTools) {\n    13→    return MethodToolCallbackProvider.builder().toolObjects(notesTools).build();\n    14→  }\n    15→}\n    16→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"tool_RfJjc02EpvEzKQgTt0ipq88l","session_id":"9c606146-0f99-4e7f-bc70-a7a06f289760","uuid":"8aeed83c-b37a-4ff8-ad5c-82c4a00c787f"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_dUpPCxTMEYaU6PI9FmYm0aZW","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→server:\n     2→  port: ${NOTES_MCP_HTTP_PORT:${SERVER_PORT:8080}}\n     3→\n     4→spring:\n     5→  autoconfigure:\n     6→    exclude:\n     7→      - org.springframework.boot.autoconfigure.data.neo4j.Neo4jDataAutoConfiguration\n     8→  ai:\n     9→    mcp:\n    10→      server:\n    11→        enabled: true\n    12→        stdio: false\n    13→        protocol: STREAMABLE\n    14→        name: notes-mcp\n    15→        version: 0.1.0\n    16→        type: SYNC\n    17→        annotation-scanner:\n    18→          enabled: false\n    19→        instructions: |\n    20→          Notes MCP управляет сохранением и поиском текстовых заметок в общей базе.\n    21→          Перед добавлением убедитесь, что заголовок кратко отражает содержание, а теги помогают дальнейшему поиску.\n    22→        capabilities:\n    23→          tool: true\n    24→          resource: false\n    25→          prompt: false\n    26→          completion: false\n    27→      streamable-http:\n    28→        mcp-endpoint: /mcp\n    29→        keep-alive-interval: 30s\n    30→    openai:\n    31→      enabled: true\n    32→      api-key: ${OPENAI_API_KEY:demo-openai-key}\n    33→      base-url: ${OPENAI_BASE_URL:https://api.openai.com/v1}\n    34→      embedding:\n    35→        options:\n    36→          model: ${NOTES_EMBEDDING_MODEL:text-embedding-3-small}\n    37→          dimensions: ${NOTES_EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS:1536}\n    38→  datasource:\n    39→    url: ${NOTES_MCP_DB_URL:jdbc:postgresql://localhost:5432/ai_advent}\n    40→    username: ${NOTES_MCP_DB_USER:ai_advent}\n    41→    password: ${NOTES_MCP_DB_PASSWORD:ai_advent}\n    42→    driver-class-name: org.postgresql.Driver\n    43→  jpa:\n    44→    open-in-view: false\n    45→    hibernate:\n    46→      ddl-auto: validate\n    47→    properties:\n    48→      hibernate:\n    49→        dialect: org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQLDialect\n    50→        format_sql: true\n    51→  liquibase:\n    52→    change-log: classpath:db/changelog/notes/db.changelog-master.yaml\n    53→    contexts: ${NOTES_LIQUIBASE_CONTEXTS:notes}\n    54→\n    55→notes:\n    56→  embedding:\n    57→    model: ${NOTES_EMBEDDING_MODEL:text-embedding-3-small}\n    58→    dimensions: ${NOTES_EMBEDDING_DIMENSIONS:1536}\n    59→  search:\n    60→    default-top-k: ${NOTES_SEARCH_TOP_K:5}\n    61→    min-score: ${NOTES_SEARCH_MIN_SCORE:0.55}\n    62→  storage:\n    63→    vector-table: ${NOTES_VECTOR_TABLE:note_vector_store}\n    64→    schema-validation: ${NOTES_VECTOR_SCHEMA_VALIDATION:true}\n    65→  validation:\n    66→    max-title-length: ${NOTES_MAX_TITLE_LENGTH:160}\n    67→    max-content-length: ${NOTES_MAX_CONTENT_LENGTH:4000}\n    68→    max-tags: ${NOTES_MAX_TAGS:25}\n    69→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"tool_RfJjc02EpvEzKQgTt0ipq88l","session_id":"9c606146-0f99-4e7f-bc70-a7a06f289760","uuid":"1ca4872e-4447-4074-9152-6b0ec3ac0807"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"msg_JhKBBg5Zm0MKKAjJOQm9TAX7","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"tool_gDwNXqfqrRwblICPe40vQ9Zo","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/Users/griogrii_riabov/grigorii_projects/ai_advent_challenge_new/frontend/src/components/ActiveProfileBanner.tsx"}}],"model":"kimi-for-coding","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":58162,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available","prompt_tokens":58162,"cached_tokens":0},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":"tool_RfJjc02EpvEzKQgTt0ipq88l","session_id":"9c606146-0f99-4e7f-bc70-a7a06f289760","uuid":"cfd443f8-6ea8-416f-bc7d-61df30a0dc9a"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"tool_gDwNXqfqrRwblICPe40vQ9Zo","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→import { useEffect, useMemo, useState } from 'react';\n     2→import {\n     3→  createDevLink,\n     4→  loadActiveProfile,\n     5→  loadActiveProfileAudit,\n     6→} from '../lib/profileActions';\n     7→import { buildProfileKey, useProfileStore } from '../lib/profileStore';\n     8→import type {\n     9→  DevProfileLinkResponse,\n    10→  ProfileAuditEntry,\n    11→  UserProfileDocument,\n    12→} from '../lib/profileTypes';\n    13→import './ActiveProfileBanner.css';\n    14→\n    15→const formatTimestamp = (value?: string) => {\n    16→  if (!value) {\n    17→    return '—';\n    18→  }\n    19→  try {\n    20→    return new Date(value).toLocaleString();\n    21→  } catch (error) {\n    22→    return value;\n    23→  }\n    24→};\n    25→\n    26→const resolveProfileShortInfo = (profile?: UserProfileDocument | null) => {\n    27→  if (!profile) {\n    28→    return '—';\n    29→  }\n    30→  const parts = [profile.locale, profile.timezone].filter(Boolean);\n    31→  return parts.join(' · ');\n    32→};\n    33→\n    34→const ActiveProfileBanner = () => {\n    35→  const profile = useProfileStore((state) => state.profile);\n    36→  const namespace = useProfileStore((state) => state.namespace);\n    37→  const reference = useProfileStore((state) => state.reference);\n    38→  const channel = useProfileStore((state) => state.channel);\n    39→  const setChannel = useProfileStore((state) => state.setChannel);\n    40→  const devToken = useProfileStore((state) => state.devToken);\n    41→  const setDevToken = useProfileStore((state) => state.setDevToken);\n    42→  const auditEvents = useProfileStore((state) => state.auditEvents);\n    43→  const isAuditLoading = useProfileStore((state) => state.isAuditLoading);\n    44→  const auditError = useProfileStore((state) => state.auditError);\n    45→  const isLoading = useProfileStore((state) => state.isLoading);\n    46→  const [bannerStatus, setBannerStatus] = useState<string>('');\n    47→  const [initialLoadRequested, setInitialLoadRequested] = useState(false);\n    48→  const [devTokenDraft, setDevTokenDraft] = useState(devToken ?? '');\n    49→  const [devLink, setDevLink] = useState<DevProfileLinkResponse | null>(null);\n    50→  const [isGeneratingLink, setGeneratingLink] = useState(false);\n    51→  const profileKey = buildProfileKey(namespace, reference);\n    52→\n    53→  useEffect(() => {\n    54→    setDevTokenDraft(devToken ?? '');\n    55→  }, [devToken]);\n    56→\n    57→  const availableChannels = useMemo(() => {\n    58→    const options = new Set<string>(['web', 'telegram']);\n    59→    if (channel) {\n    60→      options.add(channel);\n    61→    }\n    62→    profile?.channels.forEach((entry) => {\n    63→      if (entry?.channel) {\n    64→        options.add(entry.channel);\n    65→      }\n    66→    });\n    67→    return Array.from(options.values()).sort();\n    68→  }, [channel, profile?.channels]);\n    69→\n    70→  const channelOverrides = useMemo(() => {\n    71→    if (!profile) {\n    72→      return null;\n    73→    }\n    74→    return profile.channels.find((entry) => entry.channel === channel) ?? null;\n    75→  }, [profile, channel]);\n    76→\n    77→  const describeEvent = (entry: ProfileAuditEntry) => {\n    78→    const metadata = (entry.metadata ?? {}) as Record<string, unknown>;\n    79→    switch (entry.eventType) {\n    80→      case 'profile_created':\n    81→        return `Профиль создан (v${metadata.version ?? '—'})`;\n    82→      case 'profile_updated':\n    83→        return `Профиль обновлён (v${metadata.version ?? '—'})`;\n    84→      case 'identity_attached':\n    85→        return `Привязана учётная запись ${metadata.provider ?? ''}`.trim();\n    86→      case 'identity_detached':\n    87→        return `Откреплена учётная запись ${metadata.provider ?? ''}`.trim();\n    88→      case 'role_assigned':\n    89→        return `Выдана роль ${metadata.role ?? ''}`.trim();\n    90→      case 'role_revoked':\n    91→        return `Снята роль ${metadata.role ?? ''}`.trim();\n    92→      default:\n    93→        return entry.eventType;\n    94→    }\n    95→  };\n    96→\n    97→  const renderAuditItem = (entry: ProfileAuditEntry) => (\n    98→    <li key={entry.id}>\n    99→      <span className=\"profile-banner-history-time\">{formatTimestamp(entry.createdAt)}</span>\n   100→      <span className=\"profile-banner-history-source\">{describeEvent(entry)}</span>\n   101→      {entry.channel && <span className=\"profile-banner-history-channel\"> · {entry.channel}</span>}\n   102→    </li>\n   103→  );\n   104→\n   105→  const handleReload = async () => {\n   106→    setBannerStatus('Обновляем профиль…');\n   107→    try {\n   108→      await loadActiveProfile();\n   109→      await loadActiveProfileAudit();\n   110→      setBannerStatus('Профиль и журнал обновлены');\n   111→    } catch (error) {\n   112→      setBannerStatus(\n   113→        error instanceof Error\n   114→          ? error.message\n   115→          : 'Не удалось обновить профиль',\n   116→      );\n   117→    }\n   118→  };\n   119→\n   120→  const handleSaveDevToken = () => {\n   121→    setDevToken(devTokenDraft || undefined);\n   122→    setBannerStatus('Dev token обновлён');\n   123→  };\n   124→\n   125→  const handleGenerateDevLink = async () => {\n   126→    if (!devToken) {\n   127→      setBannerStatus('Укажите dev token, чтобы сгенерировать ссылку');\n   128→      return;\n   129→    }\n   130→    setGeneratingLink(true);\n   131→    setBannerStatus('Создаём dev-link…');\n   132→    try {\n   133→      const link = await createDevLink();\n   134→      setDevLink(link);\n   135→      setBannerStatus('Dev-link сгенерирован');\n   136→    } catch (error) {\n   137→      setBannerStatus(\n   138→        error instanceof Error\n   139→          ? error.message\n   140→          : 'Не удалось создать dev-link',\n   141→      );\n   142→    } finally {\n   143→      setGeneratingLink(false);\n   144→    }\n   145→  };\n   146→\n   147→  const renderDevLink = () => {\n   148→    if (!devLink) {\n   149→      return null;\n   150→    }\n   151→    const expires = new Date(devLink.expiresAt).toLocaleString();\n   152→    return (\n   153→      <p className=\"profile-dev-link-result\">\n   154→        Код: <code>{devLink.code}</code> · канал{' '}\n   155→        {devLink.channel ?? 'any'} · истекает {expires}\n   156→      </p>\n   157→    );\n   158→  };\n   159→\n   160→  useEffect(() => {\n   161→    if (profile || initialLoadRequested) {\n   162→      return;\n   163→    }\n   164→    setInitialLoadRequested(true);\n   165→    loadActiveProfile().catch(() => {\n   166→      setBannerStatus('Не удалось загрузить профиль, попробуйте ещё раз.');\n   167→    });\n   168→  }, [profile, initialLoadRequested]);\n   169→\n   170→  useEffect(() => {\n   171→    loadActiveProfileAudit().catch(() => {\n   172→      setBannerStatus('Не удалось загрузить историю профиля.');\n   173→    });\n   174→  }, [profileKey, devToken]);\n   175→\n   176→  return (\n   177→    <section className=\"profile-banner\">\n   178→      <div className=\"profile-banner-header\">\n   179→        <div>\n   180→          <p className=\"profile-banner-title\">Активный профиль</p>\n   181→          <p className=\"profile-banner-hint\">X-Profile-Key: {profileKey}</p>\n   182→        </div>\n   183→        <div className=\"profile-banner-actions\">\n   184→          <label>\n   185→            Канал\n   186→            <select value={channel} onChange={(event) => setChannel(event.target.value)}>\n   187→              {availableChannels.map((code) => (\n   188→                <option key={code} value={code}>\n   189→                  {code}\n   190→                </option>\n   191→              ))}\n   192→            </select>\n   193→          </label>\n   194→          <button type